<exercise id="eip-216"><problem id="eip-838">
  <para id="eip-241">What is the air-fuel ratio (AFR) in an engine containing 1.67 kg of air and 1.00 mol of pure n-octane (C<sub>8</sub>H<sub>18</sub>)?</para>
